Chapter 8. Elementary UDP Sockets
*********************************

8.11 connect function with UDP
==============================

   The DNS example given mentions the file `/etc/resolv.conf' for Unix.
In Miami the corresponding configuration mechanism is the built-in `DNS
servers' database.


@EndNode

@Node "NODE_CHNINE" "TCPIP.guide/NODE_CHNINE"
