Chapter 21. Out-of-Band Data
****************************

21.2 TCP Out-of-Band Data
=========================

   AmigaOS does not have a SIGURG flag. Out-of-band data can be
detected by using the exception fd set in select().

21.3 sockatmark Function
========================

   `sockatmark' is not supported by the standard AmigaOS BSD-socket
API, but by the Miami API.


