@Toc "Main"

Chapter 27. Client-Server Design Alternatives
*********************************************

27.2 TCP Client Alternatives
============================

   The Fork()-based client implementation described in this section and
in section 27.3 cannot be used in AmigaOS unless very extensive
modifications are made.

27.5-27.12
==========

   All servers described in these sections use fork() and cannot be
used in AmigaOS unless very extensive modifications are made.

@EndNode

